{"info": {"author": "Alexey Schebelev", "author_email": "", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: BSD License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "description": "# htmlfy\nPython package for HTML minification.  \n\n## Installation\n```shell\npython3 -mpip install htmlfy\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n### Minifing HTML markup in variable\n\n```python\n>>> import htmlfy\n>>> html = \"\"\"\n    <!DOCTYPE html>\n    <html>\n      <head>\n        <title>Hello</title>\n      </head>\n      <body>\n        <p>hello, world!</p>\n      </body>\n    </html>\"\"\"\n>>> htmlfy.minify_html(html)\n'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><title>Hello</title></head><body><p>hello, world!</p></body></html>'\n```\n\n### Minifing HTML file\n\n```python\n>>> import htmlfy\n>>> src_path = 'my_file.html'\n>>> dst_path = 'my_file.min.html'\n>>> htmlfy.minify_html_file(src_path,dst_path)\n```\n\n### Arguments\n\n```python\ndef htmlfy.minify_html(html,\n                strict_spaces=True,\n                no_space_between_tags=True,\n                preserve=True,\n                remove_comments=True,\n                html5_min_attr=True,\n                html5_emptytags=True\n                )\n\ndef minify_html_file(source_path,minified_path,\n                strict_spaces=True,\n                no_space_between_tags=True,\n                preserve=True,\n                remove_comments=True,\n                html5_min_attr=True,\n                html5_emptytags=True\n                )\n```\n\n* **strict_spaces** - strict all spaces(new lines, tabs and etc.) to single space. Except preserved blocks.\n* **no_space_between_tags** - delete all spaces between tags.\n* **preserve** - it will save all formating in `<pre>`,`<textarea>`,`<script>` tags. Also it will keep PHP expresions like `<?php ... ?>` and `<?=...?>`\n* **remove_comments** - delete all types of comments from the code also from `<style>` and `<script>` like `<!-- ... -->`,`/* ... */` or `// comment`. You can save the comment using `<!--! ... -->` format. Expressions comments like `<!--[if gte IE 7]>...<![endif]-->` will be preserved also. \n* **html5_min_attr** - shrink `disabled=\"disabled\"`,`checked=\"checked\"`,`selected=\"selected\"` to HTML5 notation `disabled`,`checked` and `selected` \n* **html5_emptytags** - removes tailing slash in empty tags like `<br />`,`<img ... />` or `<input ... />`\n\n## License\n\nCopyright (c) 2019, Alexey Schebelev\n\nDistributed under [The BSD 3-Clause License](http://opensource.org/licenses/BSD-3-Clause).\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/AlexxNB/htmlfy", "keywords": "", "license": "", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "htmlfy", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/htmlfy/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/htmlfy/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/AlexxNB/htmlfy"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/htmlfy/0.1.3/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": "", "summary": "Python package for HTML minification", "version": "0.1.3", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>htmlfy</h1>\n<p>Python package for HTML minification.</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<pre>python3 -mpip install htmlfy\n</pre>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<h3>Minifing HTML markup in variable</h3>\n<pre><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">htmlfy</span>\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">html</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"\"\"</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">    &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">    &lt;html&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">      &lt;head&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">        &lt;title&gt;Hello&lt;/title&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">      &lt;/head&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">      &lt;body&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">        &lt;p&gt;hello, world!&lt;/p&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">      &lt;/body&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"s2\">    &lt;/html&gt;\"\"\"</span>\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">htmlfy</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">minify_html</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">html</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"s1\">'&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;title&gt;Hello&lt;/title&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;hello, world!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;'</span>\n</pre>\n<h3>Minifing HTML file</h3>\n<pre><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">htmlfy</span>\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">src_path</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'my_file.html'</span>\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">dst_path</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'my_file.min.html'</span>\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">htmlfy</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">minify_html_file</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">src_path</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">dst_path</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<h3>Arguments</h3>\n<pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"nf\">htmlfy</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">minify_html</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">html</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">strict_spaces</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">no_space_between_tags</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">preserve</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">remove_comments</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">html5_min_attr</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">html5_emptytags</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span>\n                <span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"nf\">minify_html_file</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">source_path</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">minified_path</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">strict_spaces</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">no_space_between_tags</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">preserve</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">remove_comments</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">html5_min_attr</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"n\">html5_emptytags</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span>\n                <span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>strict_spaces</strong> - strict all spaces(new lines, tabs and etc.) to single space. Except preserved blocks.</li>\n<li><strong>no_space_between_tags</strong> - delete all spaces between tags.</li>\n<li><strong>preserve</strong> - it will save all formating in <code>&lt;pre&gt;</code>,<code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code>,<code>&lt;script&gt;</code> tags. Also it will keep PHP expresions like <code>&lt;?php ... ?&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;?=...?&gt;</code></li>\n<li><strong>remove_comments</strong> - delete all types of comments from the code also from <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> like <code>&lt;!-- ... --&gt;</code>,<code>/* ... */</code> or <code>// comment</code>. You can save the comment using <code>&lt;!--! ... --&gt;</code> format. Expressions comments like <code>&lt;!--[if gte IE 7]&gt;...&lt;![endif]--&gt;</code> will be preserved also.</li>\n<li><strong>html5_min_attr</strong> - shrink <code>disabled=\"disabled\"</code>,<code>checked=\"checked\"</code>,<code>selected=\"selected\"</code> to HTML5 notation <code>disabled</code>,<code>checked</code> and <code>selected</code></li>\n<li><strong>html5_emptytags</strong> - removes tailing slash in empty tags like <code>&lt;br /&gt;</code>,<code>&lt;img ... /&gt;</code> or <code>&lt;input ... /&gt;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>License</h2>\n<p>Copyright (c) 2019, Alexey Schebelev</p>\n<p>Distributed under <a href=\"http://opensource.org/licenses/BSD-3-Clause\" rel=\"nofollow\">The BSD 3-Clause License</a>.</p>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 4661540, "releases": {"0.1.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "ea1278738755aff41d90e6c73c969fa9", "sha256": "a238f7498bd7d5e6c3754e39ae395edf31c2fe8b0a29d503893d849c1ac9e848"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "htmlfy-0.1.0-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "ea1278738755aff41d90e6c73c969fa9", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": null, "size": 4362, "upload_time": "2019-01-02T15:06:58", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-01-02T15:06:58.749750Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/0e/3a/5b5802e7ef06302d10c57cd8f7343f313491d3a406988c1e887727c89ec2/htmlfy-0.1.0-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "118917a99c15f65a7159b611d504ac1a", "sha256": "d2bd49870ebdfc7e78e442cc5751483db26ef17d33fc8eaa77e363f90ff1f40d"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "htmlfy-0.1.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "118917a99c15f